{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs20 
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Some artists may have a considerable back catalogue of recordings. It is generally desirable that only recordings made during the term of the agreement, indeed during the relevant contract period, are delivered in fulfilment of the minimum commitment. This is for two main reasons:
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u160\'3f
\par 
}
